name: Magaca
promo-message: Waxaa sameeyay jacayl ❤️ kooxda kooxda ee 'Hobu.com'. Qorshee safarkaaga ka dib safka safka hore hada qorsheeyaha safarka wada shaqeynta ee waqtiga dhabta ah
general-advice-wash-hands-description: Dhaq gacmahaaga si joogto ah iyo 20 ilbiriqsi adiga oo isticmaalaya saabuun iyo biyo ka dib marka aad sanka ka afuufto, qufacdo ama hindhisto iyo ka hor intaadan wax cunin ama gacanta ku haynin. Gacmaha oo si hagaagsan loo dhaqo ayaa ah habka ugu waxtarka badan ee loo dilo fayrasyada.
general-advice-minimise-contact-descript: Yaree shirarka aan muhiimka ahayn iyo safarada oo raadso beddellada salaanta sida is-gacan qaadyada, is-dhunkashada ama dhunkashada.
general-advice-avoid-face-description: Gacmuhu si sahlan ayey u qaadi karaan fayraska isla markaana marka la wasakheeyo, gacmuhu waxay u gudbin karaan fayraska indhahaaga, sankaaga ama afkaaga. Laga soo bilaabo halkaas, fayrasku jirkaaga ayuu geli karaa wuuna ku xanuunsiin karaa.
general-advice-be-hygienic-description: Ku dabool afkaaga iyo sankaaga xusulkaaga fooshka ah ama masarkaaga markaad qufacdo ama hindhisto, oo isla markiiba tuur nudaha aad isticmaashay.
general-advice-self-isolate-description: Haddii aad u yeelatid ifilada sida astaamaha waa in aad gooni u goysaa si looga hortago halista faafinta cudurka adoo guriga jooga.
